review.reviewBody: I love the Nourish Bowl! There are so many great options to choose from, and it's very tasty.
This wrap looks nothing like its picture!!!  There is no filling!!!!!! Very disappointed as i "was" a Tractor fan.
The portion is a lot less than I expected

Ok I know times are tough for restaurants, but I just paid $7.50 for a yogurt POWER PARFAIT (GF) that is literally 3 bites. The picture displayed of their yogurt parfait is completely false advertising as what you actually receive is 1/3 of the size no joke!
The salad was delicious. Will order again. Just wish they packed it a little fuller.
